Text: FW Tracking PST Original Message From mailto Sent Monday January PM To Subject Tracking I have to first apologize I gave the speakers to my shipper at work who felt he could ship the items whenever he felt up to it So I had to FedEx nd day air the speakers to you I am truly sorry Here is the tracking number go to wwwfedexcom to see where they are Thanks for you patience

FW An offer is inPST Original Message From mailto Sent Tuesday February PM To Darron Giron Subject An offer is in Dear Darron Giron Congratulations on having lenders competing for your business Your decision to make a loan request through LendingTree has really paid off and now you are in a great position to choose the offer thats best for you iwayloancom Inc has responded to your loan request You can see all the details of your offer by visiting newstatusloginasp Simply enter your email address and password to retrieve your loan offer If one of your responses is good but not good enough feel free to contact the lender directlyyou have the power to get the best deal through LendingTree As your personal customer care advocate I am dedicated to helping you find the best loan for your needs If either myself or one of my customer care teammates can help you at any time during the process please reply to this email or call us Monday through Friday ampm EST and Saturday ampm EST Thank you for using LendingTreeWhen Banks Compete You Win Bobbi Green Director of Customer Care LendingTree Inc
